### Elite Clinic Phase 0 API Test Requests

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5094
@tenantSlug = clinic-test
@token = 

### 1. Health Check (No Auth Required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. SuperAdmin Login (No Tenant Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "superadmin",
  "password": "Admin@123456"
}

### 3. Get Current User (Requires Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 5. Patient Login (Requires X-Tenant Header)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/patient/login
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant: {{tenantSlug}}

{
  "username": "patient@example.com",
  "password": "Password@123"
}

### 6. Swagger Docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger/index.html

### 7. Invalid Login (Should Return 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "invalid",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 8. Missing Tenant Header (Should Return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/patient/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "patient@example.com",
  "password": "Password@123"
}
